---
title: Sichuan-Glazed Chicken with Garlic Rice & Roasted Cashews
description: Our recipe creators have outdone themselves with this superbly tasty dish. Sichuan garlic paste and soy sauce give the chicken and veggies masses of flavour, while fluffy garlic rice is an ideal base. We aren’t sure who the real hero is in this dish – you decide!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hoisin-chicken-888065de.jpg
